import React from 'react'

export default function ContactForm() {
    return (
        <form action="/">
            <label htmlFor="form-name">Nom</label>
            <input id="form-name" type="text" placeholder="Nom" />
            <label htmlFor="form-title">Titre</label>
            <input id="form-title" type="text" placeholder="Titre" />
            <label htmlFor="form-message">Message</label>
            <input id="form-message" type="textarea" placeholder="Message" />
            <button type="submit">Envoyer</button>
            captcha
        </form>
    )
}
